About Us
.entry-header
Company Information
Rocky’s Convenience Store & Campground is located in a part of Old Florida where nature has been untouched. Where there is abundant hunting, fishing, scalloping, crabbing, bird watching, equestrian, hiking and cycling at nearby State Parks such as Hickory Mound Impoundment, Hampton Springs & Spring Creek. Just a short drive from the State Capitol and many of Florida’s freshwater springs where snorkeling, scuba diving and manatee viewing are among the favorite activities.
Rocky’s Convenience Store & Campground is American Owned and Operated and can accommodate motor homes, large or small, and has a section for tents. Grassy pull through sites, which all have full water and electric hook ups (50/30/20 amp service), picnic tables and fire rings. We have a very accessible dump station, washer & dryers, and a New large bathhouse.
Rocky’s Convenience Store is located next to the Campground and offers breakfast/lunch daily, wide variety of hunting/fishing items and other necessities. Large fueling bays for your convenience.
Come visit us at Rocky’s Convenience Store & Campground, where small town friendly and Southern hospitality is our priority.
Customer Service
Gifts
Visit our newly renovated campground with new dump station. 34 full hook-up sites (50/30/20 amp service). Free use of dump station fuel purchase. Call today to make reservations. 850-584-6600
We have a great supply of hunting, fishing and camping supplies. Stop in today and find the perfect gift for family and friends.
Global Reach
Staff Photo (to be added later)
Our Commitment
We are committed to offer our customers competitive gas prices, groceries, and quality hunting, fishing and camping supplies.
